Author: yuvadeep
Title: [ANN][SHB] ðŸ”¹ðŸ”¹ Shopiblock ðŸ”¹ðŸ”¹ Shopify on the BlockchainðŸ”¹ðŸ”¹
Body: Economists may argue that even in the worst situation merchants need to make profits; users think it is shocking to them. If merchants cannot get profits from the online business then, waste of investing thousands of dollars on it. Earlier, it is difficult for the users to compare all the reviews and prices through online. Now consumers can easily select whichever they found cheaper or will choose by following highest rating reviews. Thus, now offline stores face the problem as they cannot compete with online. SHOPIBLOCK is the first system which is particularly designed to permit merchants to allow branded cryptocurrency to a group of audiences easily. Thus, they provide many offers, loyalty points, and rewards that create an identifier to prevent illegal access from your Smartphone. SHOPIBLOCK is a branded token that can be easily traded by merchants for SBH (shopiblock), a known cryptocurrency like Bitcoin, Etehreum. SBH (shopiblock) can exchange them for real cash by the customers wherever in the world.

Author: Shopiblock
Title: [ANN][SHB] ðŸ”¹ðŸ”¹ Shopiblock ðŸ”¹ðŸ”¹ Shopify on the BlockchainðŸ”¹ðŸ”¹
Body: We know the situation of the current market. Some customers are already using cryptocurrencies as a payment option. But most don't. The reason is that cryptocurrencies are still new and not on the mass market. But this is changing with every new blockchain company/project. Some people may have fear about losing their money when using crypto as there is no protection for buyers. With Shopipal this problem can also be solved. Decentralization brings a lot of advantages we will definitly use in the future. Let's start by applying it on e-commerce.
